    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >以希腊女神之身逃离冥界</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >扮演<strong>自然女神珀尔塞福涅（Persephone）</strong>，在与冥王哈迪斯（Hades）达成协议后，寻找逃离冥界的道路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这款<strong>免费试玩版</strong>提供约<strong>45分钟的游戏时间</strong>，带你探索游戏的前两个区域——<strong>哈迪斯城堡</strong>和<strong>许普诺斯洞穴</strong>，让你初步体验本作的故事、视觉风格和核心玩法。这些内容将在完整版中进一步扩展。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201100/extras/c0435b4b6af930bef60055a4cd49ff96.poster.avif?t=1761727625\" width=609 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201100/extras/c0435b4b6af930bef60055a4cd49ff96.webm?t=1761727625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >解谜闯关</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >为了逃离冥界，你需要<strong>移动物体</strong>、利用<strong>重量与重力机制</strong>，并与<strong>平台互动</strong>以推进游戏进程。每个关卡都设置了独特的谜题挑战，融合了<strong>探索与解谜元素</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201100/extras/e312f60309e6d0bdd2602418e2d5a9d9.poster.avif?t=1761727625\" width=609 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201100/extras/e312f60309e6d0bdd2602418e2d5a9d9.webm?t=1761727625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >掌控自然之力</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用你的<strong>自然魔法</strong>来<strong>控制植物的生命周期</strong>——使其生长或枯萎，从而影响环境。通过改变自然，<strong>解开谜题</strong>、<strong>发现隐藏区域</strong>，并<strong>创造新的前进道路</strong>。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201100/extras/c2e25b048a36c70e9395a832ce9bd175.poster.avif?t=1761727625\" width=609 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201100/extras/c2e25b048a36c70e9395a832ce9bd175.webm?t=1761727625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >利用<strong>闪电蘑菇的微光</strong>暂时照亮前方道路，揭示隐藏通道，引导你穿越黑暗洞穴。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201100/extras/b8b993435032960f817f29935ffb248d.poster.avif?t=1761727625\" width=609 height=330 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201100/extras/b8b993435032960f817f29935ffb248d.webm?t=1761727625\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >重温复古游戏美学</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏画面灵感来自<strong>PS1/PS2时代</strong>，拥有<strong>低多边形建模</strong>、<strong>像素化着色器</strong>与<strong>故障纹理效果</strong>，完美还原<strong>早期3D游戏的魅力</strong>。你还可以<strong>自定义视觉风格</strong>！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>本项目获得斯洛伐克艺术委员会公共资金支持。</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3201100/extras/ea92d0fd0ae945ba1fb5d75625ebe047.avif?t=1761727625\" width=200 height=73 /></span></p>",
